Healthcare Revenue & Growth Analysis

Business Problem
Hospital management needs to understand revenue trends and 
identify services driving growth.

Dataset
- Source: Hospital operational data (anonymized)
- Records: 25,000+
- Period: 2023â€“2024

Tools Used
- Power BI
- DAX
- Excel

Key Metrics
- Revenue growth rate
- Revenue by department
- Monthly trends

Key Insights
- Surgical services contributed 42% of total revenue.
- Revenue dipped in Q3 due to reduced patient volumes.

Recommendations
- Optimize scheduling for high-performing departments.
- Investigate Q3 operational constraints.

